text: The Midleton Distillery may refer to: * The Jameson Experience, Midleton, also known as the Old Midleton Distillery, was a distillery which operated in Midleton, County Cork, Ireland from 1825 to 1975. It is now a museum and visitor centre. * The New Midleton Distillery, a new distillery built alongside the existing Old Midleton Distillery. It opened in 1975.
